---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="BharatDCIM is building India's first DCIM with native ToD tariff billing. Learn about our mission to modernize Indian data center operations."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="section-label">About Us</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Building DCIM<br />
          <span class="text-[--color-accent]">for Bharat</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We believe Indian data centers deserve tools built for Indian operations—not
          Western software with India as an afterthought.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section pt-0">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">
            Democratize DCIM<br />
            <span class="accent">for Indian Operators</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            India's data center capacity is growing from 1.4 GW to 9 GW by 2030. Yet most
            of the 150+ facilities still manage operations with Excel spreadsheets and
            manual processes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Global DCIM tools cost $100,000+ and don't understand Indian billing complexity—ToD
            tariffs, DG metering, state-wise regulations, GST compliance.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            We're building the DCIM that Indian operators actually need, at a price point
            that makes sense for mid-market facilities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">9 GW</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">India's projected data center capacity by 2030</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">150+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Data center facilities across India</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">$30B+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Committed investments in Indian DC infrastructure</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Now -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">Timing</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Why Now?<br />
          <span class="accent">The Perfect Storm</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[--color-accent]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[--color-accent]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">ToD Tariffs Mandatory</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Time-of-Day tariffs became mandatory for all commercial consumers above 10kW
            from April 2024. Every data center now needs ToD-aware billing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[--color-primary]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[--color-primary]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18 9 11.25l4.306 4.306a11.95 11.95 0 0 1 5.814-5.518l2.74-1.22m0 0-5.94-2.281m5.94 2.28-2.28 5.941" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Capacity Explosion</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            AWS, Microsoft, Reliance are investing $60B+ combined. Dozens of new facilities
            coming online need management tools from day one.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mid-Market Underserved</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
            Top 5 operators hold 75% of capacity but only 10-15% of facility count.
            120+ mid-market facilities need affordable, India-focused DCIM.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">Values</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          How We<br />
          <span class="accent">Build</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[--color-accent]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[--color-accent]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 3.75H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3.75 6v1.5M16.5 3.75H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v1.5m0 9V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-1.5m-9 0H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-1.5M15 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Focus Over Features</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We're not building another generic DCIM. We're solving one problem brilliantly:
              automated power billing with Indian tariff intelligence.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[--color-primary]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[--color-primary]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Transparent Pricing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              No hidden fees, no surprise connector costs. Simple per-rack pricing
              published on our website. Indian operators deserve clarity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 0 0 2.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 0 0 4.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 0 0-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 0 1 8.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0 1 11.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 1 1-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 0 1 6.75 0Zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 1 1-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 0 1 5.25 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Customer Partnership</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We build with our customers, not for them. Early adopters shape the roadmap.
              Your feedback directly influences what we build next.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Built in India</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Following the Freshworks playbook: build from India at a fraction of
              incumbent pricing, own a defensible niche, think globally from day one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section bg-[--color-primary] text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          Join the Journey
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
          We're looking for early adopter partners to shape the future of
          Indian data center management. Get in touch.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-light text-lg px-8 py-4">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
